<item>
            <title>[LU-17346] interop cleanup_nocli failed with 203: Memory leaks detected</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-17346</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for sarah &amp;lt;sarah@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c846c653-e24a-41f4-a3aa-dc68c895a186&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/c846c653-e24a-41f4-a3aa-dc68c895a186&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Test session details:&lt;br/&gt;
clients: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_14/2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_14/2&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-240.22.1.el8_3.x86_64&lt;br/&gt;
servers: &lt;a href=&quot;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_15/77&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://build.whamcloud.com/job/lustre-b2_15/77&lt;/a&gt; - 4.18.0-477.15.1.el8_lustre.x86_64&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;&amp;lt;&amp;lt;Please provide additional information about the failure here&amp;gt;&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;CMD: trevis-42vm3 lsmod | grep lnet &amp;gt; /dev/null &amp;amp;&amp;amp;
lctl dl | grep &apos; ST &apos; || true
CMD: trevis-42vm3 dmsetup status /dev/mapper/ost7_flakey &amp;gt;/dev/null 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
CMD: trevis-42vm3 dmsetup table /dev/mapper/ost7_flakey
CMD: trevis-42vm3 dmsetup remove /dev/mapper/ost7_flakey
CMD: trevis-42vm3 dmsetup mknodes &amp;gt;/dev/null 2&amp;gt;&amp;amp;1
CMD: trevis-42vm3 modprobe -r dm-flakey
CMD: trevis-42vm1.trevis.whamcloud.com lsmod | grep lnet &amp;gt; /dev/null &amp;amp;&amp;amp;
lctl dl | grep &apos; ST &apos; || true
[21617.235545] LustreError: 311874:0:(class_obd.c:858:obdclass_exit()) obd_memory max: 460194046, leaked: 56

mv: cannot stat &apos;/tmp/debug&apos;: No such file or directory
Memory leaks detected
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</description>
